Utilities common to all of BEL.

          Description

Class Summary
BELPathFilters BEL file filters, useful for capturing various BEL files by extension.
BELPathFilters.BELFileFilter BEL file filter for files with the .bel extension (case insensitive).
BELPathFilters.GlobalProtonetworkFilter Global proto-network filter for paths ending with the PathConstants.GLOBAL_PROTO_NETWORK_FILENAME filename.
BELPathFilters.ProtonetworkFilter Proto-network filter for directories ending with the .pn suffix (case sensitive).
BELPathFilters.XBELFileFilter XBEL file filter for files with the .xbel extension (case insensitive).
PackUtils Utilities for packing and unpacking of strings.
Pair<T,U>  
StackUtilities Utility methods for accessing and leveraging the stack-based architecture of the virtual machine.
ValidationUtilities Utilities for performing validation.
 

Enum Summary
